data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful ranch-style. This home provides 3 main level bedrooms PLUS a large upstairs bonus room w/ full bath: perfect in-law or teen suite. Entry Foyer opens to family room with fireplace & sep dining room. Beautiful kitchen overlooking the family room, breakfast bar, granite countertops, white cabinets, pantry & dining nook. Sunroom with loads of windows that have wonderful lighting. Master suite bedroom features trey ceiling, spa like bath w/ double vanity, separate tub and shower with a walk-in closets. 1.12-Acre Private wooded lot! Private wooded back yard.Top-rated schools. All three schools are less than 1 mile! Rural feel, yet close to shopping & dining with easy 316 access to Athens and Buford. NO HOA & all electric!!!
